ğŸ“ Description:
Merges another branch into the current one. Resolves changes into one history.

ğŸ”¹ 11. git pull

ğŸ’» Example:

git pull origin main


ğŸ“ Description:
Fetches changes from a remote repository and merges them into your current branch.

ğŸ”¹ 12. git push

ğŸ’» Example:

